<tr id="L6"><td><a href="#L6">6</a></td><td>DATA:  Although I am technically proficient, according to my fellow performers, I lack soul.</td></tr>

<tr id="L7"><td><a href="#L7">7</a></td><td>CRUSHER:  Data, telling us why you're going to fail before you make the attempt is never wise.</td></tr>

<tr id="L8"><td><a href="#L8">8</a></td><td>DATA:  But is not honesty always the preferred choice?</td></tr>

<tr id="L9"><td><a href="#L9">9</a></td><td>PICARD:  Excessive honesty can be disastrous, particularly in a commander.</td></tr>

<tr id="L10"><td><a href="#L10">10</a></td><td>DATA:  Indeed?</td></tr>

