<tr id="L14"><td><a href="#L14">14</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: The quartet begin Mozart's Eine Kleine Nachtmusik</td></tr>

<tr id="L15"><td><a href="#L15">15</a></td><td>RIKER [OC]:  Captain, we're receiving a message from the Sheliak Corporate.</td></tr>

