<tr id="L21"><td><a href="#L21">21</a></td><td>SHELIAK [OC]: : Federation creatures, there are humans on the fifth planet of Tau Cygna. This planet was ceded to the Corporate in section one hundred and thirty-three, paragraph seventy seven of the Treaty of Armens. We will begin settlement of this world in four days. Remove the humans.</td></tr>

<tr id="L22"><td><a href="#L22">22</a></td><td>PICARD:  What the devil?</td></tr>

<tr id="L23"><td><a href="#L23">23</a></td><td>SHELIAK [OC]:  Federation creatures, there are humans on the fifth planet</td></tr>

<tr id="L24"><td><a href="#L24">24</a></td><td>PICARD:  Cancel message.</td></tr>

