<tr id="L26"><td><a href="#L26">26</a></td><td>PICARD:  Humans can't survive in that environment. Exposure to hyperonic radiation is fatal.</td></tr>

<tr id="L27"><td><a href="#L27">27</a></td><td>RIKER:  Then the Sheliak are asking us to chase ghosts.</td></tr>

<tr id="L28"><td><a href="#L28">28</a></td><td>PICARD:  No, Number One. The Sheliak haven't broken a century of silence to send us after phantoms. An investigation is in order. Set course for Tau Cygna Five.</td></tr>

<tr id="L29"><td><a href="#L29">29</a></td><td>ANNOTATION: In orbit of the orange-brown planet</td></tr>

